name: Cecile Monina
text: Arthur's dad is Maōri, so pinoy thousands of years removed (since the theory is Polynesians migrated from the Philippines through Micronesia then Polynesia then eventually New Zealand). He is also the clone (and obviously original) from the Clone Wars.
